title: Better Homes & Gardens India - March 2016
description:
English | 132 pages | PDF | 40 Mb




Better Homes and Gardens is the Indian edition of the best selling magazine in the US. Our premise: the home is where it all comes together.Our key sections--Fresh, Indoors, Style, Living, Outdoors, Better, and Food--are loaded with useful information, the best from the market, and DIY tips and tricks to make you look your best as a mom, a wife, a fashionista, and a homemaker
